    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "FLYING SAUCER",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "Would you be so kind as to advise me whether or not it is",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "the usual procedure for agents of the FBI to investigate reports",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "of unidentified flying objects which have been seen on the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "ground.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "In several recent cases, agents of the FBI have been present",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "when USAF investigators from local AFBs in the vicinity of the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "landing site have carried out their investigations. Would you",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "also advise me whether it would be possible to obtain copies of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "reports made by agents of their findings. One case which I do",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "have a personal interest in was the La Madera April 26, 1964",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "case where a [REDACTED] age 35, of La Madera and Santa Fe,",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "New Mexico, reported to [REDACTED] that he had obser-",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "ved an unidentified object approximately 300 feet from his home.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "The following day, Agent [REDACTED] of the FBI and Major [REDACTED] of",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "text": "Kirtland AFB in Albuquerque inspected the site. Can you advise me",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "text": "of Agent [REDACTED] findings at the site?.",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 53,
      "text": "I realise that your department is probably more concerned",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 54,
      "text": "with federal crime, however, I cannot understand why it has",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 55,
      "text": "concerned itself with cases which are normally undertaken by the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56,
      "text": "USAF as a matter of National Defence.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 57,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 58,
      "text": "This letter is not intended as a letter of criticism but",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 59,
      "text": "more of a general inquiry.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
